35
00:01:52,829 --> 00:01:56,590
That&#39;s quite a popular conception of what a personality is, but it&#39;s not necessarily

36
00:01:56,590 --> 00:02:01,090
what we mean when we talk about personality in Psychology.

37
00:02:01,090 --> 00:02:04,909
